    "Other studies compared both classical machine learning as well as deep learning methods.",
    "For example, in the case of Tebar and Gopalan (42), a so-called feature fusion model that includes both deep learning (a convolutional neural network (CNN) and a BiGRU model), as well as a classical machine learning model (logistic regression classifier with handcrafted features) is used.",
